This is a responsive Login Form built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The form features a clean, centered layout with fields For email and password input, along with a Show Password toggle For user convenience. 
JavaScript handles basic validation to ensure both fields are filled before allowing login. 
Upon submission, the form displays the entered credentials using an alert, making it ideal For demonstrating front-end login functionality without a backend. 
It also includes helpful links For password recovery and user registration.

